{"TopicId":207523,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Mod to stop camera auto changing modes?","CreatedByName":"Krazy1","CreatedById":203523,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-03T03:05:39Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Krazy1","CreatedById":203523,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-03T03:05:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hate that the camera changes modes automatically, like from \u0022orbital\u0022 to \u0022free\u0022 when you go from orbital to suborbital. It\u0027s always when I\u0027m about to do a burn and the whole screen starts spinning wildly. Squad should have made this a radio button option in the settings.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-04-03T03:06:06Z\u0022 title=\u002204/03/2022 03:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EApril 3, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Krazy1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotel26","CreatedById":139095,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-03T03:12:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKnow how you feel; particularly on ascent.\u00A0 Part of my launch checklist (including from the surface of moons) is [V] to select Free mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis isn\u0027t the most annoying thing in KSP.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-03T07:43:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Emaybe\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022168379\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed768710957\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/172244-ksp-15-keep-it-straight-camera-persistent-mode-105-2018-10-19/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195p